Testing of Activity LifeCycle

Testing 1

1.) Click on Application Icon
MainActivity:onCreate
MainActivity:onStart
MainActivity:onResume

2.) Open Second Activity by clicking on Button which opens using Intent Class (onClick() {Intent i = new Intent(this, SecondActivity.class); startActivity(i);}).
MainActivity:onPause
SecondActivity:onCreate
SecondActivity:onStart
SecondActivity:onResume
MainActivity:onStop

3.) Press Back Button which will move to Main Activity
SecondActivity:onPause
MainActivity:onRestart
MainActivity:onStart
MainActivity:onResume
SecondActivity:onStop
SecondActivity:onDestroy

4.) Now we are in the Main Activity. Again Press Back Button which will Exit Application.
MainActivity:onPause
MainActivity:onStop
MainActivity:onDestroy

Testing 2

1.) Click on Application Icon
MainActivity:onCreate
MainActivity:onStart
MainActivity:onResume

2.) Press Home Button
MainActivity:onPause
MainActivity:onStop

3.) Again Click on Application Icon
MainActivity:onRestart
MainActivity:onStart
MainActivity:onResume

Testing 3

1.) Click on Application Icon
MainActivity:onCreate
MainActivity:onStart
MainActivity:onResume

2.) Open Second Activity by clicking on Button which opens using Intent Class (onClick() {Intent i = new Intent(this, SecondActivity.class); startActivity(i);}).
MainActivity:onPause
SecondActivity:onCreate
SecondActivity:onStart
SecondActivity:onResume
MainActivity:onStop

3.) Press Home Button
SecondActivity:onPause
SecondActivity:onStop

4.) Again Click on Application Icon
SecondActivity:onRestart
SecondActivity:onStart
SecondActivity:onResume

5.) Now Close the Application Using Application Switch Icon.
SecondActivity:onPause
SecondActivity:onStop
MainActivity:onDestroy
SecondActivity:onDestroy

Testing 4
1.) Click on Application Icon
MainActivity:onCreate
MainActivity:onStart
MainActivity:onResume

2.) Now Close the Application Using Application Switch Icon.
MainActivity:onPause
MainActivity:onStop
MainActivity:onDestroy